data.description: Beautiful 5 BR/3BA home in the heart of desirable Towne Lake. This home was built in 2016 so it gives you the ability to live in a newer home yet still be a part of a well established neighborhood. Lovely updated custom kitchen with granite island, eating area, and oak floors. Laundry room on main floor with custom cabinetry for extra storage. A lovely walk in custom closet can be found in the master bedroom for easy organization and storage. Beautiful covered porch on back of house where friends and family can gather. This home is a located in a highly desired swim and tennis community plus walking distance to excellent schools. Just minutes from food and shopping in downtown Woodstock. This is a must see home!
